HTVdev,provides,resources,to,develop,ideas,and,applications,within,HTC,devices,It,also,enables,connection,with,HTC,and,other,developers,Providing,HTC,Scribe,technology,with,HTC,tables,the,HTC,Scribe,Pen,API,is,a,framework,for,drawing,applications,The,framework,provides,pen,controls,settings,and,properties,that,are,available,to,the,native,applications,as,well,as,the,ability,to,interact,with,the,pen,s,buttons